{"tid":2016131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍就理大事件再落案控12人暴動 下周一上午在東區裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-05-14T07:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T08:21:05.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe02377ad2910b0292f07c8eb4571546903de11b","tid":2016131,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:33:22.000Z","msg":"警方就理大事件再落案控12人暴動<br />\n14.05.2020 15:12<br />\n<br />\n警方再就去年11月理大一帶的事件，在全港各區拘捕5男2女，連同去年拘捕後保釋候查的5人，合共12人被落案起訴參與暴動罪，下周一上午在東區裁判法院提堂。12名被起訴的人士年齡介乎18至60歲，其中3人被加控「管有工具可作非法用途」，另一人被加控「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287459&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1287459%26csid%3D261_341&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7tqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=ec100204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1287459&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9082a976f61f40a0f4ebeeeb8d784172ebb357bb","tid":2016131,"uid":272922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:47:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n得閒既記得去旁聽支持下佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9229a9c3ef4159049085cd83501df328b8887a53","tid":2016131,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:02:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85dc3b88a5fb98f4b3a510bd4e3731f7fda066fb","tid":2016131,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8825f0931cb64bf114594d86397aa9a91ccb2108","tid":2016131,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗"}]}